"943","SUB-ITEM 77E - LEGAL PROCEEDINGS"
"944","Since February 2004, Federated and related"
"945","entities (collectively, Federated) have been"
"946","named as defendants in several lawsuits, that"
"947","were consolidated into a single action in the"
"948","United States District Court for the Western"
"949","District of Pennsylvania, alleging excessive"
"950","advisory fees involving one of the Federated-"
"951","sponsored mutual funds.  Without admitting"
"952","the validity of any claim, Federated reached a"
"953","final settlement with the Plaintiffs in these"
"954","cases in April 2011."
